Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.70,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord2.25\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:09.03,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Departure - When the Snow First Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:46.45,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:49.24,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:13.69,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:22.53,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:26.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:28.35,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:32.64,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:33.96,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.97,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.00,0:23:39.97,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:45.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.71,0:23:45.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:52.18,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:57.93,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:02.57,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:45.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:47.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:51.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:54.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find them if you look hard enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:57.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like coming back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:02.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:06.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it your turn to clean the yard, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something I wanted to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:26.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's been half a year since Kanata came to the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gotten pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:31.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:32.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:40.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I can put away those old earplugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:49.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame, don't you think you should stay in town this winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:04.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been alone on this mountain for fifty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:13.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going. Keep going. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to look like a real tank now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:20.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you sure you can do the rest yourself, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about taking some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:26.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Kureha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:47.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My, why are you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:50.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You kept the military annuals here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:54.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata wanted to know more about Princess Iliya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where it would be other than there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi might have a copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask next time I see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:24.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Iliya was the first daughter of the current Archduke Arkadia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:30.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I told you before, but she was an amazing tankman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:34.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus said something like "if she were still alive" when he was here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:41.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She passed away. I think it was two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:44.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:49.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness was assigned to the royal guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:54.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but she took to wandering the country encouraging national pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:05:01.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And as she was traveling between cities, she tried to save a drowning child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:07.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a rumor, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Iliya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, it's Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:49.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She brought Yuuko here - oh, Yuuko is Martin's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:57.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But actually, an old lady named Jacquotte - she lives alone in the mountains -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:06:00.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes I buy vegetables from her in the morning -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:04.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,oh, right! Didn't you say you liked those pickled vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:08.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Jacquotte grew those vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:14.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one has seen Madame Jacquotte recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:19.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she hasn't looked very healthy, either, so they're worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:25.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she lives pretty deep in the mountains, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to whatever it is. Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:44.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that Princess Iliya was going to marry the emperor of the Holy City, Rome, to improve relations with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But then she would be the third consort!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:50.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The third one! Third!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Practically a bargaining chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:07:00.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that fell through when she passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:05.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,so we kept fighting until we struck a truce this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A half-built house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:19.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say she lived alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:31.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Yuuko sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:38.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:46.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Too good for that bratty little Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a wonderful house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:54.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I built this house myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:56.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:03.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That one is for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your son coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in a city far away now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll keep it ready for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:18.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So he and my son can feel at home anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:22.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep it ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:38.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And when will this son of yours come home, Madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter will come home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better leave the mountain before the snow starts falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:52.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:09:00.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish that house. I have no intention to move until I do, or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:00.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with this absurd act!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:07.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prepared for winter? Firewood? Food?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't prepared anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:15.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work out somehow. Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such nice girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:19.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what a stubborn old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:34.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just so similar, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:37.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that. How am I similar to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:42.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you don't say or listen to what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:51.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:57.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report in last week's regular communications.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:02.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roman forces on our eastern borders have been mobilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:10.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:15.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really? For Madame Jacquotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:30.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take these to her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:39.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you heard anything about how the conferences are going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:45.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Princess Iliya were still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:52.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait, Martin. Didn't Princess Iliya have a sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And here's ¥4,000,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:54.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First I've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:11:00.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she wasn't exactly legitimate, so it was never made public,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:04.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's third in line for the throne or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is her sister-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:15.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:19.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:25.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a little walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your village like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a normal country village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:40.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There were plenty of fields and cows and goats,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:44.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but not many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:46.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was... a bit different from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you had good parents too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell just by looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:58.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of place did you grow up in, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:05.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I grew up in a small village near the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:10.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,surrounded by beautiful lakes and forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:15.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived there with just my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:20.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A peaceful, boring life where nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:28.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My only consolation was that my sister -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:33.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,she was born from a different mother - would come to see us sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I admired her more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:43.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was brave, kind, and accepted her fate without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:46.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned the trumpet from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:50.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But she... was too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:54.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was too kind and gave her life because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:00.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here, I thought this town was a labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:11.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was lost, I came upon this place. I thought I reached some sort of goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But later I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:21.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That this was just a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:24.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I tend to get lost on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I like being lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:39.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay! Even if you're lost! Even if it's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:46.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:56.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I'm jealous of you, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could be as honest as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:30.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:35.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like her. You're just like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:40.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember bearing a beautiful daughter like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:44.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a forbidden love and bore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:50.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who might never come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:56.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And living that nightmare, my mother passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:15:01.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you decide that it was a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:11.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He promised me that he would come back someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:17.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That he would come back for me.\N I'm content with a promise like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:17.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:23.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:28.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If there were anything else, I would have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're content with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you truly happy with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I remember loving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:45.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have my memories of him.\N Because I have hope to meet him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:48.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, I'm content.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:04.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when you think it's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:28.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}When I first met you, it was snowing like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:42.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Madame was still young, Seize was a thriving resort town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:04.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She fell madly in love with the son of a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:14.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she became pregnant with his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:18.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the boy already had a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:24.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Blessing or curse, the boy's wife couldn't bear children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:29.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So the boy took her child and left for home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:36.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Promising her that he would come back for her one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:07.48,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madame! Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm this old, sometimes I think
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,if only, back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:15.70,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Madame Jacquotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Life, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,is just a cycle of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you must find something to lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:29.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you do, the pain of loss grows as much as that little happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:39.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you have memories of that happiness -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,because you have memories -
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,man lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:56.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Sorry it's at a time like this, but I found those pictures of Princess Iliya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:19:00.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when the Princess came to Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Shuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:24.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:22.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think my parents wanted me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:27.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,to find a husband and succeed the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:33.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I fell in love with the sound of that trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:37.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:42.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She was Iliya, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:47.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really did meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:53.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so wonderful. Iliya's sound echoed through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:58.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you and I met.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:04.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might have run away. To this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:08.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So at first, I didn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would leave this place one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:19.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I honestly don't want to leave this place now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:24.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I must leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's something only I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:45.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far apart we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:49.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the sound will surely echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely echo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:56.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:22:02.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata. Did I make a good role model?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:27.41,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Rio left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.41,0:22:32.71,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,She left, echoing within me forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.71,0:22:37.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}the wonderful, wonderful sound of the sky.
